  "date": "2026-01-18 00:21:00",
  "author": "吴晓波",
  "siteName": "吴晓波频道",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"25.5\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(34, 34, 34);max-height:none;text-size-adjust:inherit;z-index:auto;background-size:auto;white-space:normal;min-height:0px;float:none;outline:0px;background-repeat:repeat;top:auto;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-width:0px;background-image:none;text-decoration-color:rgb(51, 51, 51);border-style:none;height:auto;visibility:visible;bottom:auto;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:none;text-decoration-style:solid;line-height:25.5px;border-color:rgb(51, 51, 51);background-position:0% 0%;background-clip:border-box;left:auto;margin-bottom:0em;min-width:0px;\">\n   <div mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"25.5\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;line-height: 25.5px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;min-height: 0px;background-image: none;background-clip: border-box;background-size: auto;border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);bottom: auto;float: none;height: auto;left: auto;max-height: none;min-width: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);top: auto;z-index: auto;clear: none;background-position: 0% 0%;background-repeat: repeat;\">\n    <div mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"25.5\" style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;line-height: 25.5px;\">\n     <div mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"25.5\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;line-height: 25.5px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;min-height: 0px;background-image: none;background-clip: border-box;background-size: auto;border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);bottom: auto;float: none;height: auto;left: auto;max-height: none;min-width: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);top: auto;z-index: auto;clear: none;background-position: 0% 0%;background-repeat: repeat;\">\n      <div mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"25.5\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0em;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;line-height: 25.5px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;min-height: 0px;background-image: none;background-clip: border-box;background-size: auto;border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);bottom: auto;float: none;height: auto;left: auto;max-height: none;min-width: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);top: auto;z-index: auto;clear: none;background-position: 0% 0%;background-repeat: repeat;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6669921875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/pmBoItic0ByjLFXnAvDficjyMiaPtGEibZicoOcj6CV21Ufd2A4FQ1K8xpicEJCI5icAAYb4HiaeC8XeBJT7sicIvJF7rNg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"385\" data-imgfileid=\"505671368\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cdbb5d28&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FpmBoItic0ByjLFXnAvDficjyMiaPtGEibZicoOcj6CV21Ufd2A4FQ1K8xpicEJCI5icAAYb4HiaeC8XeBJT7sicIvJF7rNg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;margin: 0px 16px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"outline:0px;color:rgb(96, 96, 96);letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;文 / 蛙小吉</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">“在i茅台抢了三天，中了两瓶1499的飞天！”最近，不少人在小红书上晒出订单。原价买到正品茅台的兴奋背后，是消费者苦“高价炒作”久矣的无奈。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">过去十几年里，</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;line-height:2em;font-family:宋体;text-align:justify;\">茅台产品在销售体系之内和体系之外，产生了两个不同的价格，业内把这种现象称为“价格双轨制”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">以53度500毫升的飞天茅台（下称“普茅”）为例：一端是被厂家严控，长期稳定在千元左右的出厂价；另一端则是被层层加码，历史峰值接近3000元的市场流通价。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">巨额利差，导致消费者们想用1499元的官方指导价买到“普茅”，比春运抢票还难。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">投机的狂欢，养肥了套利者，却透支了品牌的价值与口碑，压抑了“品鉴、宴饮、收藏”的真实需求。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">为了终结这场迷失的盛宴，贵州茅台打出了一系列推进市场化改革的“组合拳”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">在小红书上晒单的消费者们，正是赶上了1月1日“普茅”登陆i茅台的“首班车”。这个动作，曾被外界解读为一次针对黄牛和传统渠道的“战术奇袭”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;padding: 0.5em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkgh81bkpm8\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6051660516605166\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"813\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"505671308\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f1d53989&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FpmBoItic0ByhgQfSM9CCYDC6Cfib4nULTUgiazWTrUSnoFHXZSgzia51cpGARMVNqoRDk9iaECFTqNV1bm5ZUpY9NiaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">不过，单点爆破并不足以扭转顽固运行了多年的利益格局，更系统的顶层设计随后出炉。1月13日，贵州茅台董事会审议通过《2026年贵州茅台酒市场化运营方案》（下称“方案”），这标志着茅台的自我革命正式从“战术试探”阶段，迈入“战略总攻”阶段。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">这场“刀刃向内”的改革，将指向何处？这又会对“厂、商、客”三方造成什么影响？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1109375\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;height:auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"505626200\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6dc450e4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FpmBoItic0BygqDvOxagAEHH9IYgLYQP6qOGTibtcpDZGIXcTTnyHJayoekgiak1ic2yiaGIUuib6ReMpJSA2rsZSpClQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">重构利益格局，</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">打造更健康的消费生态</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">只有追溯走过的路，才能客观看待当下的困境。在特定历史时期，“价格双轨制”让经销商获得大量利润，客观上促成了覆盖全国的销售网络。这带来了繁荣，也埋下了隐患。渠道核心利润来自价差而非服务，渠道外多层级的批发商异化为“囤货套利者”，导致酒价炒作盛行、终端价格失控，消费者被边缘化。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">此前的一些市场调控举措，在旧利益格局中收效甚微。怎么才能重构“厂、商、客”三方的利益关系，打破原有渠道套利生态，建立健康可持续的共生新生态，重新掌握终端定价权呢？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">仅有4页的《方案》，从“产品体系、运营模式、渠道布局、价格机制”四个维度，描绘出了一张清晰的改革路径图，也从侧面展露了贵州茅台新管理层的战略野心。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">产品体系上，贵州茅台明确回归“金字塔”型结构，即以飞天为“塔基”，精品和生肖为“塔腰”，陈年和文化系列为“塔尖”，低度酒和茅台1935作为体系补充。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;padding: 0.5em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkghgiz51ipa\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5532591414944356\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1258\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"505671312\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e66189e7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FpmBoItic0ByhgQfSM9CCYDC6Cfib4nULTUoTIln3etukhQpIu46KajANOVhuQJf95fjMzNficM8OfG41ibMicxy9J7Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-indent: 0em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-align: justify;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(96, 96, 96);\">贵州茅台明确回归“金字塔”型结构</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">运营模式上，贵州茅台提出从传统“自售+经销”向“自售+经销+代售+寄售”的多维协同转型。其中“代售”“寄售”模式，均不转移产品物权，推动传统经销商向赚取佣金的“服务商”转型。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">渠道布局方面，构建批发、线下零售、线上零售、餐饮、私域“五大渠道”融合的立体网络，推动线上线下协同发展。线上渠道侧重提升运营效率与用户触达能力，线下渠道则聚焦消费转化与服务体验优化。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">价格机制改革，则是此次改革的核心与灵魂：贵州茅台明确提出构建“随行就市、相对平稳”的自营零售价格动态调整机制，其锋芒直指“价格双轨制”赖以生存的根基。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">简单来说，就是用“市场化零售价”取代“刚性出厂价”：通过i茅台等直销平台，以官方零售价作为公开、透明的新价格之锚，直接面向消费者，逐步废弃旧的出厂价标杆体系。再以此为基础，逆向、科学地测算不同模式下的经销商合同价或佣金，从根本上撼动“吃固定价差”的盈利模式。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">这意味着，传统意义上的“出厂价”作为价格标尺的历史已经终结，取而代之的是一个以市场为导向的、“多价态并存”的动态价格供给体系。这让茅台能够精细化分配利润，增强销售网络的适应性与韧性。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">此前巨额价差让利润沉淀流通环节、滋养投机链条，如今通过市场化零售价挤出泡沫，帮品牌夺回定价权，让消费者的注意力，从“炒作预期”拉回到“品饮价值”本身。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">而新的价格体系，也能引导消费者建立更健康的认知。据悉，1月15日，6款不同定价、不同年份的飞天茅台在上线i茅台后热卖。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6669921875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1024\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/pmBoItic0ByjLFXnAvDficjyMiaPtGEibZicouiapA98lwldSTDOq4axC7C3HtGtS0FfZPHl0LR7h9ghXFfrtxwFRelQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"364\" data-imgfileid=\"505671366\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=74afc831&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FpmBoItic0ByjLFXnAvDficjyMiaPtGEibZicouiapA98lwldSTDOq4axC7C3HtGtS0FfZPHl0LR7h9ghXFfrtxwFRelQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <h2 data-reactid=\"157\" style=\"-webk