icrosoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(0, 122, 170);white-space:normal;font-size:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:宋体;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">◎&nbsp;</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">其次，是企业成长的回归。旧模式下，巨额的渠道利润导致企业的不健康成长，业绩增长受制于价格炒作的博弈。新方案推动茅台将各渠道利润进行合理分配，以市场为中心重塑渠道生态，不依赖单瓶酒赚取暴利，转向服务本质，对全价值链的“掌控”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">直接触达消费者，使茅台得以积累宝贵的用户数据，深刻理解需求变化，实现从“生产驱动”到“市场与消费者驱动”的转型。这构成了其未来产品创新、精准营销和抵御风险的深层能力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&