x;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">敢于破除自身痼疾、建立更公平规则、追求长期健康生态的企业，将赢得投资者更长久的信任。这种基于治理改善和可持续增长模式的“确定性溢价”，远比“投机溢价”更为坚实和珍贵。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1109375\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;height:auto !important;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/pmBoItic0BygqDvOxagAEHH9IYgLYQP6q6oGNr4pHRJKIU7C211CDKZmSKCcf2Un18uy7cRfLWJyT5voeK5V0UQ/0?wx_fmt=gif\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"61\" data-imgfileid=\"505340247\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=47aae807&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FpmBoItic0BygqDvOxagAEHH9IYgLYQP6q6oGNr4pHRJKIU7C211CDKZmSKCcf2Un18uy7cRfLWJyT5voeK5V0UQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 122, 170);font-weight: bold;\">结语</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">在白酒行业结构性复苏的新周期中，茅台并没有因为过去的成功产生“路径依赖”，而是以极大的魄力，发起了“刀刃向内”的自我革命。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">它试图用短期的震荡与磨合，换取一个更加牢固的价值未来：让品牌扎根于真实的需求与文化，让企业成长行驶于可控的航道之上，让市场价值锚定在坚实的业绩与信任之中。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:宋体;\">这正是一切伟大企业穿越周期的必修课：不追逐转瞬即逝的浪花，而是通过深刻的自我革新，去顺应那深沉而确定性的潮流。茅台的改革，正是选择做时间的朋友，让真正的价值，在时光的沉淀中从容回归。</span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
